Package: attest
Type: Package
Title: Download and Document Data Provenance
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R:
    person("KW", "Taylor", email = "kw.taylor@pm.me",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0007-3849-1078"))
Description: Convenience functions to download data from known URLs, archive
    associated documentation, track file integrity via content hashes,
    and generate BibTeX citations. Designed for
    researchers who need reproducible records of externally sourced data,
    particularly from government and institutional sources.
